summary: This is an FBI Computer Analysis Response Team (CART) report documenting the creation of a master copy of video images extracted from hard drives seized in New York. The document is marked as law enforcement sensitive and appears to be part of digital evidence processing in the Epstein investigation.

events.title: CART Master Copy Creation
events.description: FBI Computer Analysis Response Team created a master copy of video images extracted from hard drives seized in New York.

keyFacts: FBI Computer Analysis Response Team (CART) processed video evidence from hard drives seized in New York.
A master copy of video images was created on June 21, 2021.
The document is marked as law enforcement sensitive and for official use only.
The evidence appears to be part of the Epstein investigation (referenced by EFTA document number).
The CART artwork archive contains video images from MCC NY video recordings/hard drives.
